2026-03-04 | Maximum XOR of Subarray of Size k

	Question
Given arr[] and integer k, find the maximum XOR value among all subarrays of size k.

	Approach
1.	Start by computing the XOR of the first k elements.
	This represents the XOR of the first window.
2.	Store it as the current answer.
3.	Slide the window one step to the right each time.
4.	To update the XOR efficiently:
		Remove the element leaving the window using XOR.
		Add the new element entering the window using XOR.
5.	Update the maximum XOR value after each step.
6.	Continue until all windows of size k are processed.

	Time Complexity
1.	O(n)

	Space Complexity
1.	O(1)

	Solution

class Solution {
public:
    int maxXorSubarray(vector<int>& arr, int k) {
        int n = arr.size();
        int currentXor = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < k; i++)
            currentXor ^= arr[i];

        int ans = currentXor;

        for (int i = k; i < n; i++) {
            currentXor ^= arr[i - k];
            currentXor ^= arr[i];
            ans = max(ans, currentXor);
        }

        return ans;
    }
};
